<h2 id="hyperledger-indy-getting-started">Hyperledger Indy Getting Started</h2>

<h3 id="overview">Overview</h3>

<p>5ê°œì˜ Actorê°€ ìˆë‹¤. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Government</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Faber College</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Acme Corp</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Thrift Bank</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Alice</code> ì²« 4ê°œëŠ” ì¡°ì§ì´ë©° <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Alice</code>ëŠ” <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Getting Started</code> ì˜ˆì œì—ì„œ ê·¸ë“¤ê³¼ êµë¥˜í•œë‹¤.</p>

